# Web3Forms access key for the contact form.
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com and enter the client's email (echojohnc@gmail.com).
# 2. Copy the access key they send and paste it below.
# 3. Copy this file to `.env.local` for local dev, and add the same key in
#    Vercel → Project Settings → Environment Variables for production.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key-here
